rows.name:
A Driver brought me here,
and before I knew it, my
dad and I had arrived.

rows.label: tlk41200141_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It was so... scary. My house was
burned down, and my friends...

rows.label: tlk41200141_01_msg0003
rows.name:
They said I can't go back
to Iraada Village anymore...
It's so lonely...
